ongo|\u30bd\u30ea\u30c3\u30ba|Sorizzu}}|| style=\"text-align:center;\" |  || style=\"text-align:center;\" |  || style=\"text-align:center;\" | {{y}} || style=\"text-align:center;\" |  || style=\"text-align:left;\" | [[Rikiya Koyama]] || style=\"text-align:left;\" |  [[Jamieson Price]]\n|-\n| Djeeta || {{Nihongo|\u30b8\u30fc\u30bf|J\u012bta}} || style=\"text-align:center;\" |  || style=\"text-align:center;\" |  || style=\"text-align:center;\" | {{y}}<br>{{ref|Cameo|Cameo}} || style=\"text-align:center;\" |  || style=\"text-align:left;\" | [[Hisako Kanemoto]] || style=\"text-align:left;\" | [[Erika Harlacher]]\n|-\n| Zooey || {{Nihongo|\u30be\u30fc\u30a4|Z\u014di}}|| style=\"text-align:center;\" |  || style=\"text-align:center;\" |  || style=\"text-align:center;\" | {{y}}<br><ref name=\"DLC 1.1\"/> || style=\"text-align:center;\" |  || style=\"text-align:left;\" | [[Ami Koshimizu]] || style=\"text-align:left;\" | [[Laura Post]]\n|-\n| Belial || {{Nihongo|\u30d9\u30ea\u30a2\u30eb|Beriaru}} || style=\"text-align:center;\" |  || style=\"text-align:center;\" |  || style=\"text-align:center;\" |  || style=\"text-align:center;\" | {{y}} || style=\"text-align:left;\" | [[Yoshimasa Hosoya]] || style=\"text-align:left;\" | Matthew David Rudd\n|-\n| Lyria || {{Nihongo|\u30eb\u30ea\u30a2|Ruria}} || style=\"text-align:center;\" |  || style=\"text-align:center;\" | {{y}}<br>{{ref|Cameo|Cameo<br>(Gran/Djeeta)}} || style=\"text-align:center;\" |  || style=\"text-align:center;\" |  || style=\"text-align:left;\" | [[Nao T\u014dyama]] || style=\"text-align:left;\" | [[Kira Buckland]] \n|-\n| Vyrn || {{Nihongo|\u30d3\u30a3|B\u012b|V}} || style=\"text-align:center;\" |  || style=\"text-align:center;\" | {{y}}<br>{{ref|Cameo|Cameo<br>(Gran/Djeeta/Lowain)}} || style=\"text-align:center;\" |  || style=\"text-align:center;\" |  || style=\"text-align:left;\" | [[Rie Kugimiya]] || style=\"text-align:left;\" | [[Sandy Fox]] \n|-\n| Elsam || {{Nihongo|\u30a8\u30eb\u30bb\u30e0|Erusemu}} || style=