-17}}</ref>\n\n{{clear}}\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n*{{Official website|http://granbluefantasyvs.com/}}\n\n{{Cygames}}\n\n[[Category:Arc System Works games]]\n[[Category:Esports games]]\n[[Category:Fantasy video games]]\n[[Category:Fiction about magic]]\n[[Category:Fiction about monsters]]\n[[Category:Fighting games]]\n[[Category:Fighting games used at the Evolution Championship Series tournament]]\n[[Category:Granblue Fantasy]]\n[[Category:Japan-exclusive video games]]\n[[Category:Multiplayer video games]]\n[[Category:PlayStation 4 games]]\n[[Category:Single-player video games]]\n[[Category:Video games based on Arthurian legend]]\n[[Category:Video games developed in Japan]]\n[[Category:Video games featuring female protagonists]]\n[[Category:Video games featuring protagonists of selectable gender]]\n[[Category:Windows games]]\n[[Category:Unreal Engine games]]\n\n{{Fighting-videogame-stub}}\n", "name_user": "Aerkdude", "label": "safe", "comment": "", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Granblue_Fantasy_Versus"}
